+	// STAMINA PENALTY: Frame-rate compensated penalty (pow method)
+	// ============================================================================
+	// Root cause of "forward push" feeling:
+	//   - Previous implementation waited for accumulator >= 10ms
+	//   - First 5 frames: no penalty, speed = 250
+	//   - Frame 6: sudden penalty, speed = 187.5
